import React from 'react'; import Card from './card/Card' import "./App.css"; import Title from './Title' const App = () =>{ return(
<div className="price-details"> <Title title="Price details" /> <div className="items"> <p>Price 2 items </p> <p>Deliver charges </p> <p>Amount Payable </p> </div> <div className="prices"> <p>1519</p> <p>0 </p> <p>1519 </p> </div> </div> <Title title="Payment details" /> <div className="card-div"> <div> <input type="radio"/><label>UPI Payment</label> </div> <div><input type="radio"/> <label> Credit/Debit/ATM card </label></div> <Card/> </div> <button className="button"> Continue to place order</button> </div> <div className="about" > <p>Indian Crafts</p> </div> </div> ) } export default App;
